text: Nomos 4000 (, "Law 4000") is a 1962 Greek drama movie directed by Giannis Dalianidis and starring Zoi Laskari, Kostas Voutsas, Eleni Zafeiriou, Vangelos Voulgaridis, Vasilis Diamantopoulos. ==Other websites== * Category:1962 drama movies Category:Greek movies Category:Movies directed by Giannis Dalianidis
title: Law 4000
